{"id":306,"date":"2014-03-10T18:01:52","date_gmt":"2014-03-10T18:01:52","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/mann.vamtam.com\/?p=306"},"modified":"2019-02-21T13:40:47","modified_gmt":"2019-02-21T13:40:47","slug":"social-recruiting","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/mann.vamtam.com\/social-recruiting\/","title":{"rendered":"Social Recruiting"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"fl-builder-content fl-builder-content-306 fl-builder-global-templates-locked\" data-post-id=\"306\"><div class=\"fl-row fl-row-full-width fl-row-bg-none fl-node-58b3685791fab fl-row-bg-attachment-scroll\" data-node=\"58b3685791fab\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-row-content-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"fl-row-content fl-row-fixed-width fl-node-content\">\n\t\t\n<div class=\"fl-col-group fl-node-58b368579203b\" data-node=\"58b368579203b\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"fl-col fl-node-58b3685792093 fl-col-has-cols\" data-node=\"58b3685792093\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-col-content fl-node-content\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-module fl-module-rich-text fl-node-58b3685792167\" data-node=\"58b3685792167\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-module-content fl-node-content\">\n\t\t<div class=\"fl-rich-text\">\n\t<p>Did you know that more than 3 billion people use social media? That\u2019s 40% of the world\u2019s population! A stat like that is why more talent acquisition teams are looking to social recruiting to try to reach candidates.<\/p>\n<p>While we know active and passive candidates are using social media, there\u2019s so much we still need to learn about how to attract and engage talent effectively on Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, Snapchat, etc.<\/p>\n<p>The Social Recruiting Strategies Conference (#SRSC) is held twice a year to offer fresh ideas from practitioners who are a bit ahead of the pack in using social media. I had the opportunity to attend my first #SRSC last week in San Francisco. What I learned is that no one has social recruiting completely figured out, and I found that comforting.<\/p>\n<p>In HR and TA there always seems to be a new strategy, a new technology or a new channel that suddenly becomes a buzzword, and we\u2019re still trying to understand what it means to us when the next buzzword comes along. (At Rally, we like to break down buzzwords, so here\u2019s our explanation of social recruiting for beginners.)<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"fl-col-group fl-node-58fcf3a265777 fl-col-group-nested\" data-node=\"58fcf3a265777\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"fl-col fl-node-58fcf3a265afe fl-col-small\" data-node=\"58fcf3a265afe\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-col-content fl-node-content\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-module fl-module-photo fl-node-58fcf3717ac08 fl-visible-desktop\" data-node=\"58fcf3717ac08\" data-progressive-animation=\"move-from-left\" data-vamtam-animation-options=\"{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;progressive&quot;,&quot;origin&quot;:&quot;center center&quot;,&quot;exit&quot;:false,&quot;delay&quot;:0,&quot;mobile&quot;:false,&quot;pin&quot;:false,&quot;pinTrigger&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-module-content fl-node-content\">\n\t\t<div class=\"fl-photo fl-photo-align-center\" itemscope itemtype=\"http:\/\/schema.org\/ImageObject\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-photo-content fl-photo-img-jpg\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"fl-photo-img wp-image-15528 size-thumbnail vamtam-lazyload-noparent\" src=\"https:\/\/mann.vamtam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/picture-05-350x350.jpg\" alt=\"Shot of two businesspeople having a discussion with colleagues blurred in the background\" itemprop=\"image\" height=\"350\" width=\"350\" title=\"What do you do?...\"  sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, (min-width: 1260px) 466px,37vw\" srcset=\"data:image\/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns=&quot;http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg&quot;%20viewBox=&quot;0%200%201300%201151&quot;%20height=&quot;1151px&quot;%20width=&quot;1300px&quot;\/&gt;\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/mann.vamtam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/picture-05-350x350.jpg 350w, https:\/\/mann.vamtam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/picture-05-100x100.jpg 100w\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"fl-col fl-node-58fcf3a265b4b\" data-node=\"58fcf3a265b4b\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-col-content fl-node-content\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-module fl-module-vamtam-heading fl-node-58fcf3807f298\" data-node=\"58fcf3807f298\" data-progressive-animation=\"move-from-right\" data-vamtam-animation-options=\"{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;progressive&quot;,&quot;origin&quot;:&quot;center center&quot;,&quot;exit&quot;:false,&quot;delay&quot;:0,&quot;mobile&quot;:false,&quot;pin&quot;:false,&quot;pinTrigger&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-module-content fl-node-content\">\n\t\t<h2 class=\"vamtam-heading \">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"vamtam-heading-line vamtam-heading-line-left\"><\/span>\n\t\n\t\n\t<span class=\"vamtam-heading-text\">The fact<\/span>\n\n\t\n\t\t\t<span class=\"vamtam-heading-line vamtam-heading-line-right\"><\/span>\n\t<\/h2>\n\t<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"fl-module fl-module-vamtam-heading fl-node-58fcf3b232cd3\" data-node=\"58fcf3b232cd3\" data-progressive-animation=\"fade\" data-vamtam-animation-options=\"{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;progressive&quot;,&quot;origin&quot;:&quot;center center&quot;,&quot;exit&quot;:false,&quot;delay&quot;:0,&quot;mobile&quot;:true,&quot;pin&quot;:false,&quot;pinTrigger&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-module-content fl-node-content\">\n\t\t<h3 class=\"vamtam-heading \">\n\t\n\t\n\t<span class=\"vamtam-heading-text\">@Social<\/span>\n\n\t\n\t<\/h3>\n\t<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n<div class=\"fl-module fl-module-rich-text fl-node-5983749353516\" data-node=\"5983749353516\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-module-content fl-node-content\">\n\t\t<div class=\"fl-rich-text\">\n\t<p>The fact that 3 billion people are using social media is a good enough reason for talent acquisition leaders to put more resources towards figuring out social recruiting. I often hear members of the Rally community say they started their Recruitment Marketing career by becoming responsible for sharing their company\u2019s careers content and job opportunities through social. A question I always ask is:<\/p>\n<p>Do you have dedicated social channels for careers, or are you sharing careers content on your company\u2019s corporate channels?<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"fl-col-group fl-node-58fcf62dbeacc fl-col-group-nested\" data-node=\"58fcf62dbeacc\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"fl-col fl-node-58fcf62dbf061 fl-col-small\" data-node=\"58fcf62dbf061\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-col-content fl-node-content\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-module fl-module-photo fl-node-58fcf633d6762 fl-visible-desktop\" data-node=\"58fcf633d6762\" data-progressive-animation=\"move-from-left\" data-vamtam-animation-options=\"{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;progressive&quot;,&quot;origin&quot;:&quot;center center&quot;,&quot;exit&quot;:false,&quot;delay&quot;:0,&quot;mobile&quot;:false,&quot;pin&quot;:false,&quot;pinTrigger&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-module-content fl-node-content\">\n\t\t<div class=\"fl-photo fl-photo-align-center\" itemscope itemtype=\"http:\/\/schema.org\/ImageObject\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-photo-content fl-photo-img-jpg\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"fl-photo-img wp-image-15530 size-thumbnail vamtam-lazyload-noparent\" src=\"https:\/\/mann.vamtam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/picture-07-350x350.jpg\" alt=\"Members of the press talking amongst themselves before a press conference\" itemprop=\"image\" height=\"350\" width=\"350\" title=\"Touching base before the conference\"  sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, (min-width: 1260px) 466px,37vw\" srcset=\"data:image\/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns=&quot;http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg&quot;%20viewBox=&quot;0%200%201300%20972&quot;%20height=&quot;972px&quot;%20width=&quot;1300px&quot;\/&gt;\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/mann.vamtam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/picture-07-350x350.jpg 350w, https:\/\/mann.vamtam.